---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken Parmigiana & Potato Wedges with Cucumber Garden Salad
description: Craving a twist on a classic? Our chicken parmigiana brings bold flavours with a Tex-Mex kick, paired with crispy potato wedges and a cool cucumber garden salad. It’s the ultimate fusion feast that’s as fun as it is delicious!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
